\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "LeeStewart1990"

\end_inset

 to study two-dimensional instability.
 The authors considered dependence of the degree of overdrive on the stability
 spectrum and found that the number of unstable modes decreases when the
 degree of overdrive increases.
 They also investigated stability of detonation with large heat release
 and varying activation energy.
 Finally, they investigated how detonation stability depends on heat release
 and found that the lower heat release is the more stable detonation becomes.
 They also demonstrated that even in the cases when detonation is stable
 to longitudinal perturbations, it can still be unstable to transverse perturbat
ions.
\end_layout

